NIDS: Detecting Unbalanced Network Traffic Intrusions with Deep Learning
Overview
Welcome to the Network Intrusion Detection System (NIDS) project, which focuses on detecting unbalanced network traffic intrusions using advanced deep learning techniques. This project implements the methodologies discussed in the paper:

S. Pavithra and K. Venkata Vikas, "Detecting Unbalanced Network Traffic Intrusions With Deep Learning," in IEEE Access, vol. 12, pp. 74096-74107, 2024.
Access the paper here
DOI: 10.1109/ACCESS.2024.3405187

